stock drop, you knew about the news in advance: Seems kind of like insider =
trading, huh?</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Or: If you=C2=A0<em>didn=E2=
=80=99t=C2=A0</em>commit the murder, but know that you are a suspect, and y=
