=80=99t prove you did it, but you sold stock, can they get you for insider =
trading?</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I don=E2=80=99t know? Seems like a=
 stretch.(Did you have some fiduciary=C2=A0obligation to the company or its=
